Package game

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.Tile
  • public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
    A cell in the 2D map. Each tile has an object (PermWall, for example). We also store a list of beings that are in this tile to allow quick lookup of beings near an area (see BeingsManager).
